high_descs: Turn left and go to the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink.
Move to the right side of the sink.
Put the knife in the sink.
Move to the left side of the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato.
Turn right and go to the microwave.
Cook the slice of potato in the microwave and pick it back up.
Turn right and go to the fridge.
Put the slice of potato in the middle of the second shelf in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Grab the knife from the sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Re-position slightly to the right.
Place the knife in the sink.
Go back to the previous position.
Grab a potato slice from the sink.
Turn right and face the microwave and fridge.
Warm the potato slice for one second.
Walk to the front of the fridge.
Place the potato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a warmed potato slice in the fridge.

high_descs: Go around the island to the kitchen sink.
Pick up the knife out of the sink.
Cut up the potato with the knife.
Walk to the other side of the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Go back to the potato.
Pick up the slice of potato.
Walk over to the microwave.
Cook the potato slice in the microwave.
Take the potato slice to the fridge.
Place the potato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked potato slice in the fridge.
